，拜登曾表示他不确定政府是否会禁止 TikTok。美反华议员谋划全面封杀 TikTok，美媒：毫无意义的政治闹剧"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "62 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/587086366"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIzbnc8PLh0NV9EAMaCDkyNzQ1MjQ2INmsgKAGMAA4FEAhcgk1ODcwODYzNjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "34_1677830889.4142904", "card_id": "Q_584098253", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "护肤之后到底需不需要洗脸?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "晚上护肤用的水、乳、精华，两个小时后要休息了脸上仍然有些许粘粘的（但是比刚抹完已经干了挺多了）是皮肤吸收饱和了吗？那我需不需要洗脸呢？不洗会不会闷痘啊？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "62 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/584098253"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Izbnc8PLh0NV9EAMaCDkyMDgxNDQzINTxrp8GMAA4KEAicgk1ODQwOTgyNTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1677830889.4147513", "card_id": "Q_585075150", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "春天有哪些一定要知道的日常护肤小常识？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5255c4f03df659ed8e3a3593722318fe_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "61 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/585075150"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Izbnc8PLh0NV9EAMaCDkyMjk4NjgxIJ+7yp8GMAA4KkAjcgk1ODUwNzUxNTB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1677830889.4152439", "card_id": "Q_586988035", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 58}, "target": {"title_area": {"